FIRST AMERICAN FINANCIAL Corp. E don declare one special dividend of one share of class B common stock for each share of common stock, wey be sey di joinbody dey collect am on top of Nov. 10 wey be sey na di Securities and Exchange Commission dey approve dis one as di expiration date for di registration.

Shareholders of Santa Ana, Calif., title insurance company approve di creation of dis second stock wey dem go sell give national over dicounter market, wey di company yarn sey dem go use take do acquisition, and oder tings.

